Goddess Aurora Borealis: Luminous energy streams soften gravity, reducing collision risks to 75% while doubling (x2) your astral coin yields.

Event Horizon Resonance: Fly right on the edge of a cosmic singularity! Gravitational pull launches you at 130% speed and multiplies your astral coin earnings by a massive x3.

